# Build the web UI into this folder as gzipped files, then upload it to
# LittleFS with:  pio run -t uploadfs
#
# Expected contents (gzip each so the ESP32 serves them pre-compressed):
#   index.html.gz
#   style.css.gz
#   app.js.gz
#
# The real app.js replaces the MockAPI layer with fetch() calls to the
# /api/* endpoints this firmware exposes (see README).
